{
  "stem": "8775.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were like youth parties, which were-- in Hungary, they formed at that time the Hungarian Arrow Cross Party.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was, of course, a youth movement, which, you know, was a segment of this party.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This Arrow Cross Party was headed by a guy by the name of Szalasi, S-Z-A-L-A-S-I, Ferenc, Franz, who was later on executed for his war crimes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was one of the biggest Nazis who took power.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After war, he was pretty much captured and put under house arraignment, or house prison.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that, that comes in later years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I'm just jumping a little bit ahead of myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But things started to turn around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I said, in-- I had to-- the normal thing was for me to, to study during the day, and then my tutor came, who was first cousin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was Farkas, Sandor, who was a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was the law clerk to my father, and worked out of his office as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went over certain material.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then after he would leave, and he would give me material from certain subjects to prepare for the next time when he came.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I had my piano lessons, and you know, practice for, for my piano lesson.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the routine was that my father normally came home from work, from court.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the afternoon, he would see his clients, and close his office, because his office and our home was all together in one place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He would close his office at 6 PM.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we would have dinner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my father and mother and myself would go out on a walk, on a leisurely-paced walk, and then we would go to the park.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
